  entry
    definition "an electronic memory device"
    examples ("a memory and the CPU form the central part of a computer to which peripherals are attached")
    id oewn-03749767-n
    partOfSpeech n
    synonyms (memory "computer memory" storage "computer storage" "memory board")
  entry
    definition "a depository for goods"
    examples ("storehouses were built close to the docks")
    id oewn-04336328-n
