    synonyms (storehouse depot entrepot storage)
  entry
    definition "keep or lay aside for future use"
    examples ("store grain for the winter" "The bear stores fat for the period of hibernation when he doesn't eat")
    id oewn-02285938-v
    partOfSpeech v
    synonyms ("hive away" "lay in" "put in" "salt away" "stack away" "stash away")
  entry
    definition "find a place for and put away for storage"
